      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add your <strong>farfalle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>farfalle</strong> for 6-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>farfalle</strong> and set aside</p><p>Tip: It doesn't need to be fully cooked, as it will go in the oven later!</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-12.01.04-1643112357111-x200.jpg",
