    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized cubes</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> cubed paneer </strong>and cook for 3-5 min until golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p><p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>golden paneer</strong> to a plate, reserving the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-12.01.04-1643112362000-x200.jpg",
