    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the paneer is browning, peel and finely dice your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic </strong>and <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice half your <strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> into rounds, then deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) the <strong>remaining chilli</strong> and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-12.01.04-1643112366092-x200.jpg",
