            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger </strong>and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
