    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>curry powder </strong>and 15g <span class=\"text-purple\">[20g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[30g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Gradually add 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong>, a little at a time, stirring frequently and cook for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains –<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> creamy curry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
