          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once smooth, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened and the spinach has wilted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-12.01.04-1643112379804-x200.jpg",
