          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-12.01.04-1643112379804-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>cooked pasta</strong>,<strong> golden paneer </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>to the sauce, season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>curried paneer & spinach pasta</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>curried paneer & spinach pasta</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong> and grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> over the top</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-15 min or until the cheese is melted and golden – this is your <strong>curried paneer & spinach pasta bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
